2014-02-25 22:52:32		[core]
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  away - toggle away status
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  bar - manage bars
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  buffer - manage buffers
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  color - define color aliases and display palette of colors
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  command - launch explicit WeeChat or plugin command
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  cursor - free movement of cursor on screen to execute actions on specific areas of screen
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  debug - control debug for core/plugins
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  filter - filter messages in buffers, to hide/show them according to tags or regex
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  help - display help about commands and options
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  history - show buffer command history
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  input - functions for command line
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  key - bind/unbind keys
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  layout - save/apply/reset layout for buffers and windows
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  mouse - mouse control
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  mute - execute a command silently
2014-02-25 22:52:32		  plugin - list/load/unload plugins
